## Compliance checklist (end of every task)

- [ ] Followed `AGENTS.md` (required on Lovable and Cursor)
- [ ] Followed `change-impact.mdc` — searched usages, traced store/hooks/routes
- [ ] Followed `team-mindset.mdc` — did not yes-man; asked if ambiguous
- [ ] Followed `git-workflow.mdc` — no commit/push unless user asked
- [ ] Followed `e2e-verification.mdc` — lint + build pass + E2E flows reported
- [ ] Followed `known-tech-debt.mdc` — did not copy listed anti-patterns
- [ ] Followed `demo-honesty.mdc` — no fake production claims
- [ ] Followed `validation-schema.mdc` if forms or input validation touched
- [ ] Followed `type-strictness.mdc` — no any, shared types FE/BE
- [ ] Followed `e2e-verification.mdc` — lint + build pass + E2E flows reported
- [ ] Followed `ui-copy-voice.mdc` if user-visible text changed
- [ ] Followed scoped rules for files touched
- [ ] Verified CS, supervisor, and owner where access control is involved

**Skipping rules is a failure.** If you cannot follow a rule, stop and tell the user why.
